  <div class="row info-list info-settings">
    <p class="col-lg-8 col-lg-offset-2">
      You are signed up for the next JavaScript Battle.  We will pull your code from the GitHub repository listed below, which you may change at any time (we will pull your most up-to-date code from your GitHub account before each battle).
    </p>
  </div>
  <div class="col-lg-8 col-lg-offset-2">
    <ul class="info-list">
      <li>
        Note #1: If you have not already forked our <a target="_blank" href="https://github.com/JSJitsu/hero-starter">hero-starter</a> repository, go to <a target="_blank" href="https://github.com/JSJitsu/hero-starter">this link</a> and click "Fork" in the top right.  If you don't do this, we won't be able to find your hero code, so your hero will just stand still for the entire battle!
      </li>
      <li>
    Note #2: If you want to change your hero code (your hero's "brain"),
    check out the <a target="_blank" href="https://github.com/JSJitsu/hero-starter">hero-starter instructions</a>.
      </li>
    </ul>
  </div>
  <div class="row">
    <form class="form-inline repoInput text-center" role="form">
      <div class="form-group">
        <label class="control-label" for="inputRepo">GitHub Repository</label>
        <input type="text" class="form-control" id="inputRepo" value="<%= get('code_repo') %>">
        <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-ok form-control-feedback"></span>
        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-default submitRepo">Save</button>
      </div>
    </form>
  </div>
  <div class="text-center">
    <a href="/logout" type="button" class="btn btn-default logoutButton">
      <i class="glyphicon glyphicon-log-out">&nbsp;</i>Log out
    </a>
  </div>